SELECT u.username, m.title, p.autoplay FROM Users u JOIN UserMovieHistory h ON u.user_id = h.user_id JOIN Movies m ON h.movie_id = m.movie_id JOIN Preferences p ON u.user_id = p.user_id WHERE h.date_watched >= '2022-01-01' AND p.autoplay = TRUE;
SELECT DISTINCT u.username, h.date_watched FROM Users u JOIN UserMovieHistory h ON u.user_id = h.user_id WHERE u.username LIKE 'J%';
SELECT u.username, m.title, m.genre FROM Users u JOIN UserMovieHistory h ON u.user_id = h.user_id JOIN Movies m ON h.movie_id = m.movie_id WHERE m.genre IN ('Action', 'Comedy');
SELECT COUNT(*) AS total_users FROM Users;
SELECT m.title, COUNT(*) AS total_watches FROM Movies m JOIN UserMovieHistory h ON m.movie_id = h.movie_id GROUP BY m.title ORDER BY total_watches DESC;
SELECT u.username, COUNT(*) AS total_watches FROM Users u JOIN UserMovieHistory h ON u.user_id = h.user_id GROUP BY u.username HAVING COUNT(*) > 5;
SELECT MAX(date_of_birth) AS oldest_user_dob FROM Users;
SELECT u.username, COUNT(*) AS total_watches FROM Users u JOIN UserMovieHistory h ON u.user_id = h.user_id GROUP BY u.username HAVING MAX(h.date_watched) >= '2022-01-01';
SELECT u.username, AVG(TO_NUMBER(EXTRACT(EPOCH FROM AGE(date_of_birth))) / 31536000) AS avg_age FROM Users u GROUP BY u.username ORDER BY avg_age DESC;

SELECT u.username, m.title, EXTRACT(MONTH FROM h.date_watched) AS watch_month FROM Users u JOIN UserMovieHistory h ON u.user_id = h.user_id JOIN Movies m ON h.movie_id = m.movie_id WHERE EXTRACT(YEAR FROM h.date_watched) = 2022;

SELECT u.username, COUNT(*) FILTER (WHERE EXTRACT(YEAR FROM h.date_watched) = 2022) AS watches_2022, COUNT(*) FILTER (WHERE EXTRACT(YEAR FROM h.date_watched) = 2023) AS watches_2023 FROM Users u JOIN UserMovieHistory h ON u.user_id = h.user_id GROUP BY u.username;

SELECT u.username, m.title, MAX(h.date_watched) - MIN(h.date_watched) AS time_between_first_last_watch FROM Users u JOIN UserMovieHistory h ON u.user_id = h.user_id JOIN Movies m ON h.movie_id = m.movie_id GROUP BY u.username, m.title;

SELECT u.username, COUNT(DISTINCT m.genre) AS unique_genres_watched FROM Users u JOIN UserMovieHistory h ON u.user_id = h.user_id JOIN Movies m ON h.movie_id = m.movie_id GROUP BY u.username ORDER BY unique_genres_watched DESC;

SELECT u.username, p.theme, SUM(CASE WHEN m.genre = 'Action' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS action_watches FROM Users u JOIN Preferences p ON u.user_id = p.user_id JOIN UserMovieHistory h ON u.user_id = h.user_id JOIN Movies m ON h.movie_id = m.movie_id GROUP BY u.username, p.theme;

SELECT u.username, m.title, COUNT(*) AS total_watches FROM Users u JOIN UserMovieHistory h ON u.user_id = h.user_id JOIN Movies m ON h.movie_id = m.movie_id GROUP BY u.username, m.title HAVING COUNT(*) >= 3;

SELECT u.username, COUNT(*) AS total_watches FROM Users u JOIN UserMovieHistory h ON u.user_id = h.user_id GROUP BY u.username HAVING AVG(TO_NUMBER(EXTRACT(EPOCH FROM AGE(date_of_birth))) / 31536000) < 30;
SELECT u.username, AVG(DATE_PART('year', CURRENT_DATE) - DATE_PART('year', date_of_birth)) AS avg_age FROM Users u GROUP BY u.username ORDER BY avg_age;
SELECT u.username, COUNT(*) AS total_watches FROM Users u LEFT JOIN UserMovieHistory h ON u.user_id = h.user_id GROUP BY u.username HAVING COUNT(h.movie_id) = 0;

SELECT u.username, COUNT(DISTINCT m.genre) AS unique_genres_watched FROM Users u JOIN UserMovieHistory h ON u.user_id = h.user_id JOIN Movies m ON h.movie_id = m.movie_id WHERE DATE_PART('year', h.date_watched) = DATE_PART('year', CURRENT_DATE) GROUP BY u.username ORDER BY unique_genres_watched DESC;
